      "en-US": {
        "description": "Tap to hop between pillars in a serene, endless arcade adventure. Play as a brave pair of circles on a journey to find their true meaning.\n\nKeep your rhythm flowing with a profound ambient soundtrack that soothes your mind. Intuitive one-handed, one-tap controls mean you can play anywhere, anytime — no Wi-Fi required.\n\n• Endless one-tap gameplay that's easy to learn, hard to master\n• Minimalist visuals and a calming ambient soundtrack\n• Test your timing and reflexes across infinite pillars\n• Game Center leaderboards to compete with friends\n• Free to play, completely offline, no ads interrupting your flow",
